Additionally, the presented experimental results for BTBO:Nd3+ powders were supported by the following analysis and calculations. As mentioned above, the LCQ effect and shortening of the lifetime τ for BTBO:Nd3+ powders strongly depend on the concentration NA of active Nd3+ ions, which can be calculated using the following equation:6NA=3ZxV\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
